{"tid":423813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"慎入!有圖! 網民熱話：16隻小強托盤開餐　中大食堂蔚為奇觀","createTime":"2017-10-04T08:16:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T17:58:36.000Z","uid":16697,"like":121,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"b8bc31e62b55ad8a16bf82600ddfb629f7780131","tid":423813,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:16:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171004/photo/bkn-20171004145440154-1004_00822_001_01p.jpg?20171004153554\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171004%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171004145440154-1004_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20171004153554&h=502228a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171004/photo/bkn-20171004145440154-1004_00822_001_02p.jpg?20171004153554\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171004%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171004145440154-1004_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20171004153554&h=083c818f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171004/photo/bkn-20171004145440154-1004_00822_001_03p.jpg?20171004153554\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171004%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171004145440154-1004_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20171004153554&h=8919e4a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大學飯堂以「頹飯」聞名，想不到連衞生情況也令人歎為觀止。上月有網民就直擊，中文大學其中一間學生食堂的一疊托盤罅隙間，布滿多列不知死活的小蟑螂。連拍片者亦不禁叫大呼：「嘩！真係精彩！」食肆藏污納垢並非新鮮事，可能「眼不見為乾淨」作罷，但如果密集式的小強就在食客眼前，學生哥又能否接受？<br />\n<br />\n上月Facebook專頁「CUHK Secrets」上載一條，於香港中文大學其中一間學生食堂拍攝到的短片。片中正拍攝食堂內一疊供學生使用的用餐托盤。近鏡一攝，發現竟有至少16隻小蟑螂潛伏在多個托盤的罅隙之間，當中有小蟑螂仍在擺動觸鬚。小蟑螂全家仝人在托盤開餐，令拍片者不禁高呼：「嘩！真係精彩！」<br />\n<br />\n事件震驚了不少中大學生，有學生戲謔指該食堂的食物以清淡食物為主，沒想到竟然有如此「高蛋白質」的食材，令人嘆為觀止。又有人指食堂「望落唔算污糟」，但想不到竟有人這麼多蟑螂，有食客上月在同一食堂用膳時，亦發現飯內有蟑螂殘肢。不過亦有勇士稱「咪又係照食！」東網曾致電該飯堂，惟對方指負責人不在不作回覆。<br />\n<br />\n網民有話說<br />\n<br />\nBen Wan： 好似幾高蛋白質咁喎！<br />\n<br />\nSam Jones：點解成日用嘅托盤都可以養到小強？<br />\n<br />\nPeter Cheung：有咩問題先！你估間間咁足料！<br />\n<br />\nAmm Ch：其實係焗住食&hellip;&hellip;差都唔係第一日&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171004/bkn-20171004145440154-1004_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171004%2Fbkn-20171004145440154-1004_00822_001.html&d=lTlDmaOwc5TUNbs8m0aHRJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=b5db4a73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171004/bkn-20171004145440154-1004_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"6864e2281149f194f35ac9793987b97cca75300a","tid":423813,"uid":7033,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:17:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f371e0c4cdce777b299b00fd8a9c1c38083a50e","tid":423813,"uid":52006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:17:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d908a7ec1f705d31580116de6cf1bcdcd5929f91","tid":423813,"uid":76776,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:21:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"68a071bb7a10ca617b0bc021309ee314a3bb7ab1","tid":423813,"uid":121130,"like":325,"dislike":1,"score":324,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:53:14.000Z","msg":"16隻小強去野餐"},{"pid":"b32821d3effadd7dcd5b7da55171cc097bd342cf","tid":423813,"uid":38737,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:54:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>16隻小強去野餐</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"100f9eaaff7c96701cb007adebd1ada2608ac0fe","tid":423813,"uid":86893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:55:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fac